{"id":3173,"name":"Risk of Rain","slug":"risk-of-rain","url":"https:\/\/www.igdb.com\/games\/risk-of-rain","created_at":1384734070254,"updated_at":1545047401428,"summary":"Risk of Rain is an action platformer\/adventure game with randomized elements.While we don\u2019t want to spoil the story, we can let a few things through! The game is set in the distant future, where space transportation is common. Space trains carry passengers and goods all across space. A particular space train, however, had some very special cargo. Through a series of unfortunate events, this space train gets shot out of orbit and crash lands on a mysterious planet.. with one survivor. \n \nThe big feature of our game is the randomized elements. The position you spawn on the map, which map you spawn on, the location of chests, enemy spawns, item spawns and more are all randomly chosen by the AI Director! We also have a massive amount of content in our game: we have 100 unique items planned, all with interesting effects. No +HP or +DAMAGE, but chance to spawn missiles and stop time. You have the option of choosing between 10 characters, all with their own different moveset. \n \nAnother thing that\u2019s important in our game is that as time increases, so does difficulty. Represented in a bar on the HUD, every minute increases the enemies\u2019 power and spawn count, developing a great sense of urgency.","rating":82.5077658669749,"popularity":10.33333333333333,"aggregated_rating":85,"aggregated_rating_count":4,"total_rating":83.75388293348746,"total_rating_count":48,"rating_count":44,"games":[26855,3222,14593,27771,9806,28952,55038,25300,24426,28240],"tags":[1,17,18,21,268435464,268435468,268435481,268435487,268435488,536871075,536871208,536871298,536871328,536871338,536871450,536871490,536871817,536871882,536872070,536872211,536872406,536872617,536872879,536872894,536872961,536872997,536873066,536873405,536874398,536875047,536875203,536875299,536875304,536875305,536875358,536875483,536875484,5